The paper deals with using document similarity methods to identify unreported links between ClinicalTrials.gov and PubMed. This involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques, which are commonly used in the fields of information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and digital libraries (cs.DL). The paper also involves data analysis and database management, which are relevant to the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB) and computers and society (cs.CY).
